name: Matthew McDaniel
text: This is my favorite pizza delivery restaraunt! Their prices are great and they have all sorts of options to choose from! Anything from feeding 1 to hosting a party, they have it! They also have exceptional service that is fast and polite. Everyone I have spoken to has been kind and helpful.

name: Phillip Reed
text: Good place.. Prices are bit high. Reason I'm giving a 4 star cus I asked for cheese on top and when I got there to pick up they forgot but I made sure they did.

name: Daniel Gary
text: It was expensive and not great for the price .The inside of the business reeked of smoke and was dirty.  I'm sure some of the Fox's pizza places are nice, but avoid this one.

name: Cendy Johnson
text: We as a family of 10. Enjoy the menu and if it's not on there they try their best to get it done. The food is amazing and the staff is awesome and friendly

name: Joey Burdin
text: I've order from this place several time out of convenience but the pizza isn't very good and delivery takes a long time... if something is wrong they don't seem to want to make it right. Delivery drivers have always been friendly though.

name: RICK Wainner
text: The pizza is great took sometime to get it but it was worth it and was served with a smile great for a once a week supper

name: billy Williams
text: Ordered Hoagies from tasted great plenty of food

name: Jamie Barrett
text: Great deals. We like the fact it is close and reasonably priced.

name: Jade Miller
text: Best pizza I have ever had

name: Janci Rice
text: Very friendly.  Even in the rain

name: Whitney Aitkens
text: This place is a joke. A kid is running the store, no adults around and they waited until we got there to pick up our order to decide to make it. After we had waited 45 minutes to come pick it up, and they made no effort to make it right.
